Software needed:
	- Needs SciPy, numpy, matplotlib, haskell
		* TO INSTALL ON UBUNTU *
		> sudo apt-get install python-scipy python-numpy python-matplotlib ghc

		* TO INSTALL ON OS X (with fink)*
		> fink install scipy-py27 matplotlib-py27 ghc

	- Needs python-cluster, basemap
		* TO INSTALL ON UBUNTU *
		> sudo apt-get install ghc python-cluster libgeos-dev
		> sudo pip install http://sourceforge.net/projects/matplotlib/files/matplotlib-toolkits/basemap-1.0.1/basemap-1.0.1.tar.gz/download

		* TO INSTALL ON OS X (with fink)*
		> fink install libgeos2
		> sudo easy_install install http://sourceforge.net/projects/matplotlib/files/matplotlib-toolkits/basemap-1.0.1/basemap-1.0.1.tar.gz/download
